                </div>

                <div class="mx-auto max-w-xs px-8">
                  <p class="mt-6 flex items-baseline justify-center gap-x-2">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight ">$19</span>
                    <span class="text-sm/6 tracking-wide ">AUD</span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-base">Monthly</p>
                  <button
                    type="button"
                    class="btn btn-secondary m-4 rounded-full uppercase"
                    aria-label="Begin your 7-day free trial with no credit card required"
                  >
                    Start 7-Day Free trial
                  </button>
                  <p class="text-xs/5 mt-6 ">
                    Pay no money now.
                    <span class="font-semibold">
                      Your subscription only begins after your free trial ends.
                    </span>
                    Cancel your subscription at anytime.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
      Dating for grown-ups. Find your soulmate in Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth and countless other cities. Verified Australian profiles only.
      Safe dating with video verification. Meet real people in your suburb.
    </div>
  </Layout.section_container>
</PartnersWeb.Layouts.app>
